1211
01:03:42,819 --> 01:03:45,311
Baywatch is our team. Baywatch is our family.

1212
01:03:45,947 --> 01:03:47,279
These are the keys to our house.

1213
01:03:48,325 --> 01:03:49,406
But you've proven to me

1214
01:03:49,492 --> 01:03:51,233
